biography: Henrik aka EDOLLO is the ultimate combination of ability, creativity, and personality in a sport born from all three. The dreadlocked Swede has been winning fans for years, but opened the world’s eyes with his sagging pants and Wu-Tang callouts at the Sochi Games. Taking a step into the backcountry world Henrik has pushed the limits of skiing once again in the new film “BE Inspired”.
name: Henrik Harlaut
